---
import CivilizationTree from '../components/CivilizationTree';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="description" content="The Tree of Vines ‚Äî Civilizations as Intertwining Vines" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Civilitatum | Tree of Vines</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <nav>
        <a href="/arbor/">‚Üê Back to Home</a>
      </nav>
      <h1>üåø Civilitatum</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">A Tree Made Not of Branches, But of Living, Intertwining Vines</p>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="intro">
        <p>
          Each vine is a civilization, growing upward through time, crossing, grafting, 
          sometimes strangling, sometimes pollinating one another. Civilizations don't replace 
          one another‚Äîthey intertwine, graft, shed leaves, go dormant, and re-sprout under new names.
        </p>
        <p class="note">
          <strong>Click</strong> on any vine to open the side panel with detailed information including themes, gifts, questions, rubrics, and connections. 
          <strong>Drag</strong> to pan, <strong>scroll</strong> to zoom.
        </p>
      </div>
      <CivilizationTree client:load width={1600} height={1000} />
    </main>

    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Crimson+Text:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;1,400&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
      
      :root {
        font-family: 'Crimson Text', serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #e8ecef 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a4d2e 0%, #2d5a27 100%);
        border-bottom: 3px solid #1a3d1f;
        padding: 2rem 3rem;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        color: white;
      }

      nav {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }

      nav a {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      nav a:hover {
        color: white;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      h1 {
        font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        font-size: 3rem;
        color: white;
        margin: 0;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      }

      .subtitle {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
        margin: 0.5rem 0 0 0;
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      main {
        padding: 3rem 2rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .intro {
        max-width: 1000px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, #fafbfc 100%);
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.08), 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        border: 1px solid rgba(45, 90, 39, 0.1);
      }

      .intro p {
        margin: 1rem 0;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #2c3e2d;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      .intro p:first-child {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: #1a4d2e;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .intro .note {
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
        border-top: 2px solid rgba(45, 90, 39, 0.15);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: #5a6c5b;
        background: rgba(45, 90, 39, 0.03);
        padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
